{"tid":1529062,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"如果仲想玩政府春袋入一入黎！","createTime":"2019-09-01T16:02:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T00:22:59.000Z","uid":167634,"like":28,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"06ca32c8bbb056a849ced00b0253afe4ded3b842","tid":1529062,"uid":167634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T16:02:16.000Z","msg":"機場無可能be water,有手足話搞機鐵同埋係東涌搞路面令交通癱瘓我只能部分同意<br />\n<br />\n812我地成功癱瘓機場係因為我地有先機進入機場，依家我地已經失去先機，的確我地已經唔可以再佔領機場，搞去機場交通係唯一方法，但搞唔可以搞東涌市中心，因為絕對係死路而且和理非一定會好混亂咁逃跑，跑上山去梅窩？大量嘅人跑上山你估警狗唔識上山大搜捕？出直升機搵你都得，碼頭等你又得！<br />\n<br />\n所以我地一定唔可以走！<br />\n搞機鐵唔難，搞任何一個站就可以，而且唔洗多人，可以be water!<br />\n<br />\n但搞路面，依家只有一個位可以搞！就係<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">青馬收費廣場！</span></span></strong>因為唔會有旅客走到而且路面交通一定會搞到青馬橋塞洒，警狗嘅車同路面支援都會進退兩難，除左警狗徵用機鐵係東涌方向攻向青馬大橋。民意已經企係我地個邊，只要大家堅守青馬收費廣場，全港各區市民都可以不斷加入補給、支援，青馬大橋地理上更加係國際著眼嘅地方！放催淚彈，開槍鎮壓都會一一被航拍機拍到！但前提係大家唔可以再be water，係任何消息，見到狗都唔好驚！唔係要你勇武！但唔可以只係和理非咁搞鳩機場交通！<br />\n<br />\n同意請分享！<br />\n========<br />\n代為轉發"},{"pid":"859f20d163daf974dbacfec4221645b33124621c","tid":1529062,"uid":167634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T16:02:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f92a0d6ad87f6c946a270b1f76130840431d87f9","tid":1529062,"uid":167634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T16:03:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43a217b7f8f1753179a47e6cc5afd400287fff8a","tid":1529062,"uid":167634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T16:03:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12f7100bfe5d02a73c14237d75cba11f0ff59a13","tid":1529062,"uid":257422,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T16:03:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/09/01/223606_db1fcc72048388792c25c8bdc081a00b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F09%2F01%2F223606_db1fcc72048388792c25c8bdc081a00b.gif&h=16fdca9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">全民學唱<span style=\"color: red;\">美國</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">國歌</span><br />\n</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1528828\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1528828</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大家仲記唔記得手足揮美國國旗唱美國國歌唱到Trump Trump都retweet!!!!</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/dcexaminer/status/1161305213841682439?s=09\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdcexaminer%2Fstatus%2F1161305213841682439%3Fs%3D09&d=c1rUz8TxCzzDRK4zYpKqdIWZOtE43EI%2FqUWggxD1P9E%3D&h=cf144f01\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdcexaminer%2Fstatus%2F1161305213841682439%3Fs%3D09&h=72f77df1\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/dcexaminer/status/1161305213841682439?s=09</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">如果十月一我地再幫支共賀一賀佢，搞到全美國都知支共國慶我地用美國國歌慶祝，你話會激到維尼幾咁高興？</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw其實就無話要等到十月一既，<br />\n黎緊每次發夢都可以唱！！！！<br />\n<br />\n但大佬大家真係要練一練佢<br />\n事關首歌音域廣、歌詞繞口<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">MV with Lyrics: </span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/vPKp29Luryc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FvPKp29Luryc&d=c1rUz8TxCzzDRK4zYpKqdIWZOtE43EI%2FqUWggxD1P9E%3D&h=d78f233c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/vPKp29Luryc</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">歌詞：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<em><span style=\"color: red;\">Oh, say can you see by the dawn's early light</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">What so proudly we hailed at the twilight's last gleaming?</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Whose broad stripes and bright stars through the perilous fight,</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">O'er the ramparts we watched were so gallantly streaming?</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">And the rocket's red glare, the bombs bursting in air,</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">Gave proof through the night that our flag was still there.</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Oh, say does that star-spangled banner yet wave</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">O'er the land of the free and the home of the brave?</span><br />\n</em><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F1sKkdk.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF1sKkdk.gif&h=5c4ce310&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nLiberate Hong Kong, <br />\nthe Revolution of Our Times"},{"pid":"22419bfcdda914e48415db3507abeef99105b804","tid":1529062,"uid":167634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T16:03:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01de4e9f71e620126f9da3c07165272531dabf65","tid":1529062,"uid":167634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T16:04:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08dc431be8f4e62762337122e6a2c19f6c9add72","tid":1529062,"uid":167634,"lik